                        <div class="font-inter font-normal text-gray-2 ">We may change the Privacy Policy from time to time due to changes on our Website or the Service or any other reason which requires us to do so; therefore, we recommend you check the Privacy Policy on a regular basis. In case of material changes, we will notify you (if you are already a customer and you have provided us your contact details) by sending you an email.</div>
